{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01DCGGYE6fx4i7ABzGrPL12b","type":"tool_result","content":"FILE: ./src/main/resources/META-INF/resources/lineItem-template.xhtml\n<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8' ?>\n<!--\n\n    Copyright (c), Eclipse Foundation, Inc. and its licensors.\n\n    All rights reserved.\n\n    This program and the accompanying materials are made available under the\n    terms of the Eclipse Distribution License v1.0, which is available at\n    https://www.eclipse.org/org/documents/edl-v10.php\n\n    SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-3-Clause\n\n-->\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html lang=\"en\"\n      xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"\n      xmlns:ui=\"jakarta.faces.facelets\"\n      xmlns:h=\"jakarta.faces.html\">\n    <h:head>\n        <title>Order Persistence Example</title>\n        <h:outputStylesheet library=\"css\" name=\"default.css\"/>\n    </h:head>\n    <body>\n        <h1><ui:insert name=\"title\">Default Title</ui:insert></h1>\n\n        <ui:insert name=\"body\">Default Body</ui:insert>\n    </body>\n</html>\n\n---END OF FILE---\nFILE: ./src/main/resources/META-INF/resources/lineItem.xhtml\n<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8' ?>\n<!--\n\n    Copyright (c), Eclipse Foundation, Inc. and its licensors.\n\n    All rights reserved.\n\n    This program and the accompanying materials are made available under the\n    terms of the Eclipse Distribution License v1.0, which is available at\n    https://www.eclipse.org/org/documents/edl-v10.php\n\n    SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-3-Clause\n\n-->\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html lang=\"en\"\n      xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"\n      xmlns:f=\"jakarta.faces.core\"\n      xmlns:h=\"jakarta.faces.html\"\n      xmlns:ui=\"jakarta.faces.facelets\">\n        <ui:composition template=\"/lineItem-template.xhtml\">\n\n            <ui:define name=\"title\">Line Items for Order #{orderManager.currentOrder}</ui:define>\n            <ui:define name=\"body\">\n                <h:form>\n                    <h:dataTable var=\"lineItem\"\n                                 summary=\"Table of line items\"\n                                 value=\"#{orderManager.lineItems}\"\n                                 rules=\"all\"\n                                 cellpadding=\"5\">\n                        <h:column>\n                            <f:facet name=\"header\">\n                                <h:outputText value=\"Item ID\" />\n                            </f:facet>\n                            <h:outputText value=\"#{lineItem.itemId}\" />\n                        </h:column>\n                        <h:column>\n                            <f:facet name=\"header\">\n                                <h:outputText value=\"Quantity\" />\n                            </f:facet>\n                            <h:outputText value=\"#{lineItem.quantity}\" />\n                        </h:column>\n                        <h:column>\n                            <f:facet name=\"header\">\n                                <h:outputText value=\"Vendor Part Number\" />\n                            </f:facet>\n                            <h:outputText value=\"#{lineItem.vendorPart.vendorPartNumber}\" />\n                        </h:column>\n                    </h:dataTable>\n                    <br />\n\n                    <h:dataTable id=\"orderPartsTable\"\n                                 summary=\"Table of parts\"\n                                 value=\"#{orderManager.newOrderParts}\"\n                                 var=\"part\"\n                                 rules=\"all\"\n                                 cellpadding=\"5\">\n                        <h:column>\n                            <f:facet name=\"header\">\n                                <h:outputText value=\"Part Number\" />\n                            </f:facet>\n                            <h:outputText value=\"#{part.partNumber}\" />\n                        </h:column>\n                        <h:column>\n                            <f:facet name=\"header\">\n                                <h:outputText value=\"Revision\" />\n                            </f:facet>\n                            <h:outputText value=\"#{part.revision}\" />\n                        </h:column>\n                        <h:column>\n                            <f:facet name=\"header\">\n                                <h:outputText value=\"Vendor Part Number\" />\n                            </f:facet>\n                            <h:outputText value=\"#{part.vendorPart.vendorPartNumber}\" />\n                        </h:column>\n                        <h:column>\n                            <f:facet name=\"header\">\n                                <h:outputText value=\"Add To Order\" />\n                            </f:facet>\n                            <h:commandButton value=\"Add\" action=\"#{orderManager.addLineItem}\">\n                                <f:setPropertyActionListener target=\"#{orderManager.selectedPartNumber}\" value=\"#{part.partNumber}\" />\n                                <f:setPropertyActionListener target=\"#{orderManager.selectedPartRevision}\" value=\"#{part.revision}\" />\n                                <f:setPropertyActionListener target=\"#{orderManager.selectedVendorPartNumber}\" value=\"#{part.vendorPart.vendorPartNumber}\" />\n                            </h:commandButton>\n                        </h:column>\n                    </h:dataTable>\n                    <br />\n\n                    <h:commandButton value=\"Back To Orders\" action=\"order\" />\n                </h:form>\n            </ui:define>\n\n        </ui:composition>\n</html>\n\n---END OF FILE---\nFILE: ./src/main/resources/META-INF/resources/order-template.xhtml\n<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8' ?>\n<!--\n\n    Copyright (c), Eclipse Foundation, Inc. and its licensors.\n\n    All rights reserved.\n\n    This program and the accompanying materials are made available under the\n    terms of the Eclipse Distribution License v1.0, which is available at\n    https://www.eclipse.org/org/documents/edl-v10.php\n\n    SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-3-Clause\n\n-->\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html lang=\"en\"\n      xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"\n      xmlns:ui=\"jakarta.faces.facelets\"\n      xmlns:h=\"jakarta.faces.html\">\n    <h:head>\n        <title>Order JPA Example</title>\n        <h:outputStylesheet library=\"css\" name=\"default.css\"/>\n    </h:head>\n    <body>\n        <h1><ui:insert name=\"title\">Default Title</ui:insert></h1>\n\n        <ui:insert name=\"body\">Default Body</ui:insert>\n\n        <h2>View All Orders</h2>\n        <ui:insert name=\"ordersTable\">Default ordersTable</ui:insert>\n\n        <h2>Create New Order</h2>\n        <ui:insert name=\"newOrderForm\">Default new orders form</ui:insert>\n\n        <h2>Find Vendors</h2>\n        <ui:insert name=\"findVendorForm\">Default find vendors form</ui:insert>\n\n        <ui:insert name=\"findVendorTable\">Default find vendor table</ui:insert>\n    </body>\n</html>\n\n---END OF FILE---\nFILE: ./src/main/resources/META-INF/resources/order.xhtml\n<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8' ?>\n<!--\n\n    Copyright (c), Eclipse Foundation, Inc. and its licensors.\n\n    All rights reserved.\n\n    This program and the accompanying materials are made available under the\n    terms of the Eclipse Distribution License v1.0, which is available at\n    https://www.eclipse.org/org/documents/edl-v10.php\n\n    SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-3-Clause\n\n-->\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html lang=\"en\"\n      xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"\n      xmlns:f=\"jakarta.faces.core\"\n      xmlns:h=\"jakarta.faces.html\"\n      xmlns:ui=\"jakarta.faces.facelets\">\n    <ui:composition template=\"/order-template.xhtml\">\n        <ui:define name=\"title\">Order Java Persistence Example</ui:define>\n        <ui:define name=\"body\">\n\n        </ui:define>\n\n        <ui:define name=\"ordersTable\">\n\n            <h:dataTable\n                var=\"order\"\n                summary=\"Table of orders\"\n                value=\"#{orderManager.orders}\"\n                rules=\"all\"\n                cellpadding=\"5\">\n                <h:column>\n                    <f:facet name=\"header\">\n                        <h:outputText value=\"Order ID\" />\n                    </f:facet>\n                    <h:form>\n                        <h:commandLink id=\"order_id_link\" action=\"lineItem\">\n                            <h:outputText value=\"#{order.orderId}\" />\n                            <f:setPropertyActionListener target=\"#{orderManager.currentOrder}\" value=\"#{order.orderId}\" />\n                        </h:commandLink>\n                    </h:form>\n                </h:column>\n                <h:column>\n                    <f:facet name=\"header\">\n                        <h:outputText value=\"Shipment Info\" />\n                    </f:facet>\n                    <h:outputText value=\"#{order.shipmentInfo}\" />\n                </h:column>\n                <h:column>\n                    <f:facet name=\"header\">\n                        <h:outputText value=\"Status\" />\n                    </f:facet>\n                    <h:outputText value=\"#{order.status}\" />\n                </h:column>\n                <h:column>\n                    <f:facet name=\"header\">\n                        <h:outputText value=\"Last Updated\" />\n                    </f:facet>\n                    <h:outputText value=\"#{order.lastUpdate}\" />\n                </h:column>\n                <h:column>\n                    <f:facet name=\"header\">\n                        <h:outputText value=\"Discount\" />\n                    </f:facet>\n                    <h:outputText value=\"#{order.discount}%\" />\n                </h:column>\n                <h:column>\n                    <f:facet name=\"header\">\n                        <h:outputText value=\"Actions\" />\n                    </f:facet>\n                    <h:form>\n                        <h:commandLink value=\"Delete\" actionListener=\"#{orderManager.removeOrder}\" action=\"order\">\n                            <f:param name=\"deleteOrderId\" id=\"deleteOrderId\" value=\"#{order.orderId}\" />\n                        </h:commandLink>\n                    </h:form>\n                </h:column>\n            </h:dataTable>\n        </ui:define>\n\n        <ui:define name=\"newOrderForm\">\n            <h:form>\n                <h:outputLabel for=\"orderIdInputText\" rendered=\"true\" value=\"Order ID: \" />\n                <h:inputText id=\"orderIdInputText\" required=\"true\" value=\"#{orderManager.newOrderId}\" /><br />\n\n\n                <h:outputLabel for=\"shipmentInfoInputText\" rendered=\"true\" value=\"Shipment Info: \" />\n                <h:inputText id=\"shipmentInfoInputText\" required=\"true\" value=\"#{orderManager.newOrderShippingInfo}\" /><br />\n\n                <h:outputLabel for=\"statusMenu\" rendered=\"true\" value=\"Status: \" />\n                <h:selectOneMenu id=\"statusMenu\" required=\"true\" value=\"#{orderManager.newOrderStatus}\">\n                    <f:selectItem itemValue=\"Y\" itemLabel=\"Complete\" />\n                    <f:selectItem itemValue=\"N\" itemLabel=\"Pending\" />\n                </h:selectOneMenu><br />\n\n                <h:outputLabel for=\"discountMenu\" rendered=\"true\" value=\"Discount: \" />\n                <h:selectOneMenu id=\"discountMenu\" required=\"true\" value=\"#{orderManager.newOrderDiscount}\">\n                    <f:selectItem itemValue=\"0\" itemLabel=\"0 %\" />\n                    <f:selectItem itemValue=\"5\" itemLabel=\"5 %\" />\n                    <f:selectItem itemValue=\"10\" itemLabel=\"10 %\" />\n                    <f:selectItem itemValue=\"15\" itemLabel=\"15 %\" />\n                    <f:selectItem itemValue=\"20\" itemLabel=\"20 %\" />\n                    <f:selectItem itemValue=\"25\" itemLabel=\"25 %\" />\n                    <f:selectItem itemValue=\"30\" itemLabel=\"30 %\" />\n                    <f:selectItem itemValue=\"35\" itemLabel=\"35 %\" />\n                    <f:selectItem itemValue=\"40\" itemLabel=\"40 %\" />\n                </h:selectOneMenu><br />\n\n                <h:commandButton value=\"Submit\" action=\"#{orderManager.submitOrder}\" />\n            </h:form>\n\n        </ui:define>\n\n        <ui:define name=\"findVendorForm\">\n            <h:form>\n                <h:outputLabel for=\"findVendorInputText\" rendered=\"true\" value=\"Search for Vendors: \" />\n                <h:inputText id=\"findVendorInputText\" value=\"#{orderManager.vendorName}\" required=\"true\" />\n                <h:commandButton id=\"findVendorButton\" action=\"#{orderManager.findVendor}\" value=\"Find Vendor\" />\n            </h:form>\n        </ui:define>\n\n        <ui:define name=\"findVendorTable\">\n            <h:dataTable var=\"vendor\" \n                         summary=\"Table of vendors\"\n                         value=\"#{orderManager.vendorSearchResults}\"\n                         rules=\"all\"\n                         cellpadding=\"5\"\n                         rendered=\"#{!orderManager.findVendorTableDisabled}\">\n                <h:column>\n                    <f:facet name=\"header\">\n                        <h:outputText value=\"Vendor\" />\n                    </f:facet>\n                    <h:outputText value=\"#{vendor.name}\" />\n                </h:column>\n            </h:dataTable>\n\n        </ui:define>\n    </ui:composition>\n</html>\n\n---END OF FILE---\nFILE: ./src/main/resources/META-INF/resources/resources/css/default.css\n/**\n * Copyright (c), Eclipse Foundation, Inc. and its licensors.\n *\n * All rights reserved.\n *\n * This program and the accompanying materials are made available under the\n * terms of the Eclipse Distribution License v1.0, which is available at\n * https://www.eclipse.org/org/documents/edl-v10.php\n *\n * SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-3-Clause\n */\nbody {\n    background-color: #ffffff;\n    font-size: 12px;\n    font-family: Verdana, \"Verdana CE\",  Arial, \"Arial CE\", \"Lucida Grande CE\", lucida, \"Helvetica CE\", sans-serif;\n    color: #000000;  \n    margin: 10px;\n}\n\nh1 {\n    font-family: Arial, \"Arial CE\", \"Lucida Grande CE\", lucida, \"Helvetica CE\", sans-serif;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #AFAFAF; \n    font-size:  16px;\n    font-weight: bold;\n    margin: 0px;\n    padding: 0px;\n    color: #D20005;\n}\n\na:link, a:visited {\n  color: #045491;\n  font-weight : bold;\n  text-decoration: none;\n}\n\na:link:hover, a:visited:hover  {\n  color: #045491;\n  font-weight : bold;\n  text-decoration : underline;\n}\n\nth {\n    font-weight: bold;\n    text-align: center;\n}\n\ntd {\n    text-align: center;\n}\n---END OF FILE---","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01YSVUfzj2BgQiP9RTpE9gbG","session_id":"937f5c14-6c2e-425e-831b-fd6be18e2599","uuid":"4794d1d9-793a-441c-9fb3-01f867c9ac97"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-3-5-haiku-20241022","id":"msg_bdrk_01SQaxZfdE1uy4x1aw9rjUA5","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01C66hm1ZK6sugBGQghTcvtk","name":"Read","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__persistence__order__spring__quarkus/run_1/output/README.md"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4257,"cache_read_input_tokens":21406,"output_tokens":104},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01YSVUfzj2BgQiP9RTpE9gbG","session_id":"937f5c14-6c2e-425e-831b-fd6be18e2599","uuid":"02fd2108-941a-4e76-b72a-e701db4547c1"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01C66hm1ZK6sugBGQghTcvtk","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Order Management Application - Spring Boot Version\n     2→\n     3→This is a Spring Boot conversion of the Jakarta EE Order Management application, maintaining the original JSF frontend while using Spring Boot for the backend services.\n     4→\n     5→## Features\n     6→\n     7→- **Order Management**: Create, view, and delete customer orders\n     8→- **Line Item Management**: Add parts to orders as line items\n     9→- **Part Management**: Manage parts with bill of materials (BOM) relationships\n    10→- **Vendor Management**: Search and manage vendor information\n    11→- **Vendor Part Management**: Associate parts with vendors and pricing\n    12→\n    13→## Technology Stack\n    14→\n    15→- **Spring Boot 3.2.0** - Main framework\n    16→- **Spring Data JPA** - Data access layer\n    17→- **JSF 4.0** - Web framework (maintaining original frontend)\n    18→- **H2 Database** - In-memory database for development\n    19→- **Maven** - Build tool\n    20→\n    21→## Project Structure\n    22→\n    23→```\n    24→src/main/java/com/example/orderspring/\n    25→├── entity/           # JPA entities (Part, CustomerOrder, LineItem, etc.)\n    26→├── repository/       # Spring Data JPA repositories\n    27→├── service/          # Business logic services\n    28→├── web/             # JSF managed beans\n    29→├── config/          # Spring configuration classes\n    30→└── OrderApplication.java  # Main Spring Boot application\n    31→\n    32→src/main/webapp/\n    33→├── *.xhtml          # JSF pages (copied from Jakarta version)\n    34→├── resources/css/   # CSS stylesheets\n    35→└── WEB-INF/        # Web configuration files\n    36→```\n    37→\n    38→## Key Changes from Jakarta EE Version\n    39→\n    40→1. **Dependency Injection**: Replaced `@EJB` with `@Autowired` and Spring's dependency injection\n    41→2. **Persistence**: Replaced JTA with Spring's `@Transactional` annotations\n    42→3. **Managed Beans**: Converted JSF managed beans to Spring `@Component` beans\n    43→4. **Configuration**: Replaced `persistence.xml` with Spring Boot's `application.properties`\n    44→5. **Database**: Added H2 database for development (replaces Payara's default datasource)\n    45→\n    46→## Running the Application\n    47→\n    48→1. **Prerequisites**:\n    49→   - Java 17 or higher\n    50→   - Maven 3.6 or higher\n    51→\n    52→2. **Build and Run**:\n    53→   ```bash\n    54→   cd persistence/spring/order\n    55→   mvn clean install\n    56→   mvn spring-boot:run\n    57→   ```\n    58→\n    59→3. **Access the Application**:\n    60→   - Main application: http://localhost:8080/order.xhtml\n    61→   - H2 Database Console: http://localhost:8080/h2-console\n    62→     - JDBC URL: `jdbc:h2:mem:testdb`\n    63→     - Username: `sa`\n    64→     - Password: (empty)\n    65→\n    66→## Application Features\n    67→\n    68→### Order Management\n    69→- View all orders in a table format\n    70→- Create new orders with status, discount, and shipping information\n    71→- Delete existing orders\n    72→- Navigate to line items for each order\n    73→\n    74→### Line Item Management\n    75→- View line items for a specific order\n    76→- Add parts to orders as line items\n    77→- Each line item includes quantity and vendor part information\n    78→\n    79→### Part Management\n    80→- View all available parts\n    81→- Parts can have bill of materials (BOM) relationships\n    82→- Each part can be associated with a vendor part\n    83→\n    84→### Vendor Management\n    85→- Search vendors by partial name\n    86→- View vendor information and contact details\n    87→\n    88→## Database Schema\n    89→\n    90→The application uses the same database schema as the original Jakarta EE version:\n    91→- `PERSISTENCE_ORDER_PART` - Parts table\n    92→- `PERSISTENCE_ORDER_CUSTOMERORDER` - Orders table\n    93→- `PERSISTENCE_ORDER_LINEITEM` - Line items table\n    94→- `PERSISTENCE_ORDER_VENDOR` - Vendors table\n    95→- `PERSISTENCE_ORDER_VENDOR_PART` - Vendor parts table\n    96→\n    97→## Configuration\n    98→\n    99→The application is configured through `application.properties`:\n   100→- Database connection settings\n   101→- JPA/Hibernate configuration\n   102→- JSF configuration\n   103→- Logging levels\n   104→\n   105→## Development Notes\n   106→\n   107→- The application automatically creates sample data on startup\n   108→- All original JSF pages and functionality are preserved\n   109→- The UI remains exactly the same as the Jakarta EE version\n   110→- Spring Boot provides embedded server, so no external application server is needed\n   111→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01YSVUfzj2BgQiP9RTpE9gbG","session_id":"937f5c14-6c2e-425e-831b-fd6be18e2599","uuid":"322e2a6b-040a-4aed-8d19-5aac9d04c74b"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01YSVUfzj2BgQiP9RTpE9gbG","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Comprehensive Project Overview:\n\n1. Directory Structure:\n```\n/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__persistence__order__spring__quarkus/run_1/output/\n├── .dockerignore\n├── .mvn/wrapper/maven-wrapper.properties\n├── Dockerfile\n├── README.md\n├── mvnw\n├── mvnw.cmd\n├── pom.xml\n├── src/\n│   └── main/\n│       ├── java/com/example/orderspring/\n│       │   ├── OrderApplication.java\n│       │   ├── entity/\n│       │   │   ├── CustomerOrder.java\n│       │   │   ├── LineItem.java\n│       │   │   ├── LineItemKey.java\n│       │   │   ├── Part.java\n│       │   │   ├── PartKey.java\n│       │   │   ├── Vendor.java\n│       │   │   └── VendorPart.java\n│       │   ├── repository/\n│       │   │   ├── CustomerOrderRepository.java\n│       │   │   ├── LineItemRepository.java\n│       │   │   ├── PartRepository.java\n│       │   │   ├── VendorPartRepository.java\n│       │   │   └── VendorRepository.java\n│       │   ├── service/\n│       │   │   ├── DataInitializationService.java\n│       │   │   └── OrderService.java\n│       │   └── web/\n│       │       └── OrderManager.java\n│       └── resources/\n│           ├── application.properties\n│           └── META-INF/resources/\n│               ├── lineItem-template.xhtml\n│               ├── lineItem.xhtml\n│               ├── order-template.xhtml\n│               ├── order.xhtml\n│               └── resources/\n│                   └── css/\n│                       └── default.css\n└── Dockerfile\n```\n\n2. Technology Stack:\n- Spring Boot 3.3.7\n- Spring Data JPA\n- JSF (Jakarta Faces) with PrimeFaces\n- H2 In-Memory Database\n- Maven Build Tool\n\n3. Key Components:\n- Entities: Represent database tables (CustomerOrder, LineItem, Part, Vendor, VendorPart)\n- Repositories: Spring Data JPA interfaces for database operations\n- Services: Business logic (OrderService, DataInitializationService)\n- Web Layer: JSF-based OrderManager for UI interactions\n- Configuration: application.properties for database and application settings\n\n4. Unique Features:\n- Automatic data initialization on startup\n- Bill of Materials (BOM) relationship for parts\n- Vendor and Part management\n- Order and Line Item tracking\n- In-memory database with sample data\n\n5. Application URLs:\n- Main Application: http://localhost:8081/order.xhtml\n- H2 Database Console: http://localhost:8081/h2-console\n\n6. Deployment:\n- Dockerized application with Maven build and Spring Boot run\n- Supports local development with embedded server\n- Java 17 compatibility\n\nThis Spring Boot application provides a comprehensive order management system with a persistent backend and a JSF frontend, maintaining the original Jakarta EE application's structure and functionality.\n\nWould you like me to elaborate on any specific aspect of the codebase?"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"937f5c14-6c2e-425e-831b-fd6be18e2599","uuid":"90c6d426-b20b-4051-8833-bb3f69975ed4"}
